    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been reliably maintained throughout its life. Mechanically, the engine and transmission operate smoothly without any known issues, and I have comprehensive service records available for review. The exterior shows some minor, expected wear such as small stone chips on the hood, but the paint retains a nice shine and there are no significant dents. Inside, the cabin is clean and has never been smoked in; while there is slight wear on the driver\u2019s seat bolster, all electronics, including the infotainment system and climate control, are fully functional. The tires have approximately 60% tread remaining. It\u2019s a solid, dependable car ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 33500.0,
