    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is presented in breathtaking showroom condition, meticulously maintained to satisfy even the most discerning collector. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely no swirl marks, scratches, or chips, having been kept in a climate-controlled garage and protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of creases, the dashboard is flawless, and the original carpets have been protected since day one. Every electronic feature and driver-assist system functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documenting rigorous preventative maintenance. Driven only in fair weather and never subjected to harsh road conditions, this is a rare opportunity to own a truly pristine, investment-grade example that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it was first delivered.",
      "price": 48500.0,
